# ========================================================

ESMatic modified and built with C++. Using the Gtk 3.0 GUI Toolkit. For 3D rendering it uses and supports OpenGL.
ESMatic now supports multiple types of robots.

Note :
  Main.cpp holds the mainframe for the application, there is no Mainframe.cpp in GtkESMatic.

=========================
      *App Run File*
=========================
- to run look for app "GtkMatic.exe"

=================================================================

-do not remove any dll files or lib files without them GtkMatic will not run

# Early Compile Beta

$g++ main.cpp -o GtkMatic.exe $(pkg-config --cflags --libs gtk+-3.0)

#--------------------
#  Build Enviorment

I have used Mingw64 to compile source code

# =======================
# Gtk themes for app ( if want )
Adwaita Dark :
  $GTK_THEME= Adwaita:dark ./GtkMatic

================
  *-Compiler-*
================
GtkESMatic compiles with the g++ compiler

==============
 *-standard-*
==============
GtkESMatic C++_STD = C++17



